author: ehillenius
msg: catch all instead of the specific ConversionException. As ConversionException is not a checked exception, and is not part of the interface method, it may not be immediately clear to implementors of convertors that they had to throw a ConversionException explicitly in order to have a proper message handling of TypeValidator.

author: jdonnerstag
msg: added support to add additional markup filter to preconfigured list of filters. This might be useful in cases like where the src attribute must not be empty. Because did not habe a wicket id, the Image component was not able to handle it. A markup filter however is easily able to do it. HtmlProblemFinder.java implements the issue.
